      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ca CXVII. Dseefma.\neeṇa Pamahzischina us wiṣeem Zilwekeem/\nfa teem buhṣ Kristu un wiṣa Walsibn\nflaweht/ gaddiht un teikt: 1/2."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eizeet to KUNGU wiṣ-\nfi Pagani / flawejeet\nwiṇnu wiṣi Landis.\n2. Jo wiṇna Schehlastiba un\nKUNGĀ Pateefiba irr war-\nna pahr mums muhſchigt/\nlleeluja."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Preeku pee manneem Nihdeta-\njeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Labbaki irr us to KUNGU\npatautees/ ne ka us Zilwekeem je-\nzerecht."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Labbaki irr us to KUNGU\npatautees/ ne ka us Leeleein-Kun-\ngeem zerecht."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Wiṣi Pagani mettahṣ\napkahrt manni/ bet eekṣch ta\nKUNGĀ Wahṛda griḅbu es\ntohṣ takappaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Tee mettahṣ prett mannu\nwiṣapkahrt/ bet eekṣch ta KUNG-\nGA Wahṛda griḅbu es tohṣ fa-\nkappaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Tee mettahṣ apkahrt man-\nni ka Ritteṣ / tee swelt ka Ug-\ngung Ehrkṣchfős / bet eekṣch ta\nKUNGĀ Wahṛda griḅbu es\ntohṣ fakappaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Es tohpu dauihtṣ / ka\nman krist buhṣ/ bet tas KUNGŚ\nirr mans Paligṣ."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Tas KUNGŚ irr mans\nStiprums un Dseefina/ un irr\nman par Pestifchanu."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Gawilefchanas un Pesti-\nschanas Balṣs (atskann) eekṣch\nto Taṣnu Dshwofteem/ ta\nKUNGĀ labba Rohka darra\nspehzigus Darbus."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Ta KUNGĀ labba Roh-\nka irr pa-augstinata/ ta KUNG-\nGA labba Rohka darra spehzı-\ngus Darbus."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Es ne nomirṣchu / bet\ndshwofchṇ / un isteikṣchu ta\nKUNGĀ Darbus."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Gann tas KUNGŚ\nDodooodo 2 mann"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CXVIII. Dseefma.\ner weena frahṣchna Pateifschanas. Dseefma\npar Deewa muhṣchigu Schehlastibu : 1.\nRas jawuṣ ṭaudis wiṣāṣ Behḍāṣ glahbj un\niepesti : 5. Bet ihpaschi Kristu no Mixro-\nneem uṣmohdina : 17. Un ka weenu at-\nmesfu Akmini par Stuhru Akmini darriṣ:\n22. Ar weenu Pamahzischannu / ka ikwee-\nnain tahdas Schehlastibas buhṣ preezatees/\nun Deewam par to pateift : 24. xc."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ateizeet tam KUNGam!\nBjo wiṇsch irr labs / jo\nwiṇna Schehlastiba pa-\nek muhṣchigt.\n2. Lai takka Israēls : Wiṇna\nSchehlastiba paleek muhṣchigi.\n3. Lai takka Aārona Nains :\nWiṇna Schehlastiba paleek muh-\nigt.\n4. Lai takka tee/ kas to KUNG-\nU bibstahṣ/ wiṇna Schehla-\niba paleek muhṣchigt.\n5. Js tahim Behdahim pee-\nnzu es to KUNGU / un tas\nUNGŚ atbildēja man/ un\narrija man) plattu Weetu.\n6. Tas KUNGŚ irr mans/\nne bihstohṣ/ ko warr man Zil-\neki darriht?\n7. Tas KUNGŚ irr mans/\nan palihofcht/ un es redsefchu"
    }
  ],
